  "strategy": [
    "Alternate between short forward moves and scanning rotations to maximize marker detection.",
    "Use commit states to enforce action completion and avoid oscillations.",
    "On obstacle detection, perform recovery (backward or rotate) and then scan before resuming exploration.",
    "Prioritize immediate approach to marker when seen; do not return to exploration unless marker is lost.",
    "Stop only when close to the marker (marker_close).",
    "Never allow move_forward after obstacle_front without a recovery/scan.",
    "Avoid offering both rotation directions in the same state.",
    "Ensure all uncontrollable events are handled in every state."
  ]
